- **Hypotheticals:** "What if someone..." (they mean themselves)
- **Fishing:** "I probably looked stupid" (tell me I didn't)
- **Exit signals:** "Anyway..." or "It's getting late" (I want to stop)
- **Deflection patterns:** Sudden topic changes (avoiding something)

